name: NewOrleansPelicansFlashNewsBrief
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Just add the New Orleans Pelicans Flash News Brief skill to your Alexa device. Then the next time you ask Alexa for your news, Pelicans News direct from the New Orleans Pelicans will be played with the rest of your news!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
